These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, documentary, action, mystery
1. the person watching documentary movies is between the person watching action movies and the person watching mystery movies##2
2. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | mystery | documentary | action |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, van, quad-bike, skateboard
1. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the van##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the car##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is between the person driving the van and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Transport   | van | skateboard | car | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
