1. the british is on the right of the russian##1
2. the egyptian is between the polish and the british##2
3. the russian is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |  3   |   4    |
| Nationality   | russian | british | egyptian | polish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-4::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, dannemann, alhambra, chaman
1. the alhambra-smoker is between the dannemann-smoker and the blend-smoker##2
2. the blend-smoker is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
3. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Cigar   | chaman | dannemann | alhambra | blend |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-5::.
