2. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person who's sport is surfing##2
3. the person who's sport is surfing is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person who's sport is water-polo##2
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Sport   | snowboarding | water-polo | surfing | tennis |

